Comment.val: /* Program to determine the default Model. The request can work with a client and a product flow. For the client this is done with the client product id (PPR_ID) in the request and when provided with the Profile and Strategy in the request. When no profile and/or strategy is provided in the request, this data is retrieved from the Online dossier klasse 31. For the product this is done with the product nummer (PR_PRODUCTNUMMER) and the Profile and Strategy are manditory for the product request. When a target date is provided the model is retrived via the default Life Cycle. */

Text.val: When no profile and/or strategy is provided, then look up the active profile and/or strategy from Product Investment settings
Determine the Product Id with the Product number from the client
Client Product does not exist --> Error 3595
For Product context: Profile is manditory --> Error 3593
For Product context: Strategy is monditory ---> Error 3594
When no target date is provided, determine the model from the default models
When a target date is provided, determine the default lifecycle
Determine the description of the found model
With the LifeCycleId and the target date determine the model
